find this game casual and relaxing.\n\nSTORY. ART. MUSIC.\nEnter a sprawling retro-futuristic cityscape with an original score, ensemble of voice actors and detailed hand drawn (in VR!) environments.\n\nGOOD \u2018OL ADVENTURE GAME\nBoot up that nostalgia for your favorite 90's point-and-click adventure games. Look around. Find items. Solve puzzles. Keep the past alive.\n\n\n* No robots were harmed in the making of this game.", "short_description": "The Secret of Retropolis is a VR narrative game of a new kind, a blend of classic point-and-click adventure with immersive cinematography. Embody the witty protagonist of a film noir plot. Meet unforgettable characters. Solve puzzles. Lose yourself in the retro-futuristic atmosphere."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://peanutbutton.net/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Peanut Button", "support_website_url": "http://peanutbutton.net/", "website_url": "http://peanutbutton.net/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "PUZZLE", "NARRATIVE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "462641452012006"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031587_556896002160062_6576043756821935546_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GfAS0Q4DTWUQ7kNvgF6l3PR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB8lirItZ1l36MRL6xu0SsDsL6X-5a3tMUp3yivgf-HaA&oe=66D99D21"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test